title: You Promised
itunes:title: You Promised
description:
God has given us promises in His Word--promises of healing, freedom, and wholeness. But what do we do before we have received them? In this message, learn about how to stand firm in your faith while you wait to see the fullness of God's promises come to pass in your life.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
